ently under development and 10 million sq. ft. planned for upcoming projects."><meta property="og:description" content="Hubtown Limited (formerly known as Ackruti City Limited) is one of India’s leading real estate developers, with over four decades of experience developing residential and commercial spaces and IT parks across India. The company primarily focuses on the Mumbai Metropolitan Region, Pune, and Gujarat. Hubtown has successfully delivered over 45 million sq. ft. of real estate, with an additional 20 million sq. ft. currently under development and 10 million sq. ft. planned for upcoming projects."><meta property="og:image" content="https://hubtown-live.netlify.app/images/share_asset.jpg"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"><title>Hubtown Limited | Leading Real Estate Developer in India</title><link rel="canonical" href="https://hubtown-live.netlify.app/"><link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon/favicon.ico" sizes="48x48"><link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/favicon/favicon.svg"><link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="96x96" href="/images/favicon/favicon-96x96.png"><link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png"><link rel="manifest" href="/images/favicon/site.webmanifest"><script type="module" src="/_nuxt/D-runbsS.js" crossorigin></script></head><body><!--teleport start anchor--><!--teleport anchor--><!--teleport start anchor--><!--teleport anchor--><!--teleport start anchor--><!--teleport anchor--><!--teleport start anchor--><!--teleport anchor--><!--teleport start anchor--><!--teleport anchor--><div id="__nuxt"><!--[--><div></div><!----><div class="loader fixed inset-0 bg-dark-blue z-[1000] flex justify-center items-center" data-v-f17dfb82><div class="center-wrapper flex-col opacity-0 scale-75 md:scale-100" data-v-f17dfb82><div class="relative w-fit h-fit" data-v-f17dfb82><div class="progress-text text-11 leading-1 tracking-16 font-mono text-off-blue" data-v-f17dfb82>0% </div><div class="flash-sq